column1: The 10 most common policy topics in AI legislations are: Criminal/Legal System, Education, Civil Rights, Public Health, Public Safety, Voting/Elections, Blockchain, Data Governance, Data Privacy, Emergency Management, Labor/Workforce.

The 10 least common policy topics in AI legislations are: Administrative Reorganization, Agriculture, Cybersecurity, Data Sharing, Digital Service Team, Facial Recognition, Infrastructure, Transportation/Mobility, Water/Energy, Website/Portal.
